title: Did Clint Eastwood Write “Why-I-Stick-My-Neck-Out-For-Trump” Viral Post?
subtitle: The origin of the essay, which has been attributed to many, remains murky.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: Clint Eastwood wrote the essay that begins “People message me why I stick my neck out for Trump. Why do I tarnish my reputation with a man that’s hated by so many?”
